Test_NBT_required_for_UFH_admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UFH admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UFH admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80724783\">About the University of Fort Hare (UFH) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80724784\"><strong>How to Apply for UFH Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80724785\">Documents Required for UFH Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80724786\">UFH Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80724787\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80724788\">Applying for Financial Assistance in UFH<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80724789\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UFH admission 2024?<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-university-of-fort-hare-ufh-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_University_of_Fort_Hare_UFH_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80724783\"><\/a>About the University of Fort Hare (UFH) Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the University of Fort Hare(UFH) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80724784\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for UFH Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/ienabler.ufh.ac.za\/pls\/prodi41\/gen.gw1pkg.gw1view\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/li>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-ufh-admission-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_UFH_Admission_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80724785\"><\/a>Documents Required for UFH Admission Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"ufh-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"UFH_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80724786\"><\/a>UFH Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee of R120.00 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R120.00<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<li>R250.00 LATE APPLICATION FEE:<strong> 01 NOVEMBER \u2013 30 NOVEMBER 2024<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80724787\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Friday, 29 October 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-ufh\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_UFH\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80724788\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in UFH<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nsfas.org.za\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">portal<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-ufh-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_UFH_admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80724789\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UFH admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/ienabler.ufh.ac.za\/pls\/prodi41\/gen.gw1pkg.gw1view\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"UFH Online Application 2024 for Admission into University of Fort Hare, UFH Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1150,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1149"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1149"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1149\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1149"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1149"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1149"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}